1 Magical eye --A Magical Eye is a power your character is born with and is shared along your familys bloodline containing special powers only avaliable to the bloodline

2 Basic Training --Basic Training includes your character doing simple physical exercise or training your energy in the form of Meditation or running for a long time  to train stamina endurance and speed

3 Realms --Realms are locations outside of the standerd universe and or in a new reality that either have different physics or work outside the natural order

4 Technology Tiers --Technology Tiers are how advanced either the Era is or the civilization meaning either stone age Bronze Age Iron Age etc all the way up to Gen 3 aka far in the future with extremely advanced technology
